<!-- 17 REFERENCES -->
<h2 style="font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;color:#14211B;border-top:2px solid #14211B;padding-top:14px;margin:30px 0 10px;">17 · Key references</h2>
<p style="font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.75;color:#3A443E;margin:0;">Selected primary sources behind the datasets, structures, and methods (full list in the manuscript draft):</p>
